{"tid":2111680,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"生日Q要幾多Q先夠？","createTime":"2020-07-16T16:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T01:56:07.000Z","uid":75964,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd32b97c19b8be925ec6e59e515c0e735712743","tid":2111680,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n琴日小妹30大壽正式變成輕熟女<br />\n咁岩佢屋企人去左隔離營<br />\n所以屋企得番佢自己一個<br />\n跟住尋晚，佢煮心型牛扒俾我食，見到佢咁落力我已經濕哂，成地都係水<br />\n<br />\n我係背後攬住佢，問佢：不如黎個生日Q？<br />\n佢錫左我一啖問我：bb想要幾多Q呀？<br />\n我：我30歲，30Q唔過份啦<br />\n<br />\n我地由夜晚7點做到今日夜晚7點<br />\n詳細就自行想像<br />\n只可以講係幾開心 <br />\n最後我屌到佢起哂漿<br />\n佢仲大叫「好舒服呀，你屌到我硬哂呀」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家我bb俾我屌到不舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問燒賓周係咪有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a36829fea594e0e918a9db892dd6e8d4fffe0a","tid":2111680,"uid":65378,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"請你唔好咁痴線"},{"pid":"27626c2f356b0a4a8bc136334fe1e6b5e48b43b2","tid":2111680,"uid":326758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"請你唔好咁痴線"},{"pid":"679ee4d52d74f1eb73c1012ecb14b16d0bba2ab7","tid":2111680,"uid":225422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:58:36.000Z","msg":"男人老狗叫自己小妹<br />\n大過啦，搞基就搞基<br />\n同性戀好正常，成熟啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92252078dc7ed7b7e4156d1a83134e7a0478ea13","tid":2111680,"uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"輕熟女又點樣屌人呢請問?"},{"pid":"ba7bd9443f69491dbed3d5bd84eb7bc5fa6d08d2","tid":2111680,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"92252078dc7ed7b7e4156d1a83134e7a0478ea13","tid":2111680,"uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"輕熟女又點樣屌人呢請問?"},"cite